data.description: Welcome to your cozy oasis in Greenacres, Florida! This charming 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom townhome boasts a delightful open front porch, perfect for enjoying those warm Florida evenings. Step inside to discover a modern space featuring a sleek gas stove, water heater, and dryer for your convenience. The laminate flooring upstairs adds a touch of elegance, while the updated bathrooms offer both style and functionality. Plus, with all-new impact windows and doors, you'll enjoy peace of mind and energy efficiency year-round. Don't miss out on this inviting retreat in the heart of Greenacres! HOA maintains roof and exterior.
